# Milestone 1 – KM 0–4.5
### Duration: Month 1–Month 3
### Teams: Survey, Earthworks, Pavement, QA/QC, Bridge, Safety

## Tasks & Subtasks

### 1. Survey & Design
- Establish control points
- Chainage marking every 50 m
- Topographic survey of road + bridge
- Soil sampling & lab tests

### 2. Earthworks
- Site clearance
- Cut & fill
- Embankment formation
- Subgrade shaping & compaction
- Density tests (QA/QC)

### 3. Drainage Works
- Excavation for culverts & side drains
- Pipe laying & backfilling
- Construct concrete-lined drains
- Stone pitching & erosion control

### 4. Pavement Construction
- Sub-base placement
- Base layer placement
- Binder course (asphalt)
- Wearing course (asphalt)
- QA/QC tests

### 5. Bridge Preparation
- Bridge foundation excavation
- Reinforcement & concrete works
- QA/QC & safety checks

### 6. Road Furniture & Safety
- Install guardrails & signage
- Kilometre posts
- Traffic management


